<topic id="xproc-transformation-scenario">
  <title>XProc Transformation</title>
  <shortdesc>This type of transformation specifies the parameters and location of an XProc
    script.</shortdesc>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>Transformation Scenarios<indexterm>XProc</indexterm></indexterm>
        <indexterm>XProc transformation scenario</indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p id="p_uzl_cgk_54b">A sequence of transformations described by an XProc script can be executed with an XProc
      transformation scenario. To create an <uicontrol>XProc transformation</uicontrol> scenario,
      use one of the following methods:<ul id="ul_fln_h5g_br">
        <li id="li_vzl_cgk_54b" irina="irina">Use the <uicontrol><image href="../img/TransformConfig16.png" id="image_imp_tvv_sr"
            />Configure Transformation Scenario(s) (<shortcut
              conkeyref="reusable-oxygen-shortcuts-list/ctrl_shift_c_shortcut"
              product="author developer editor"/><shortcut
              conkeyref="reusable-oxygen-shortcuts-list/alt_shift_tc_shortcut"
              product="authorEclipse developerEclipse editorEclipse"/>)</uicontrol> action from the
          toolbar or the <menucascade product="author developer editor">
            <uicontrol>Document</uicontrol>
            <uicontrol>Transformation</uicontrol>
          </menucascade><uicontrol product="authorEclipse developerEclipse editorEclipse"
            >XML</uicontrol> menu. Then click the <uicontrol>New</uicontrol> button and select
            <uicontrol>XProc transformation</uicontrol>.</li>
        <li id="li_wzl_cgk_54b" irina="irina">Go to <menucascade>
            <uicontrol>Window</uicontrol>
            <uicontrol>Show View</uicontrol>
          </menucascade> and select <uicontrol><image href="../img/TransformConfig16.png"
              id="image_qvk_tvv_sr"/>Transformation Scenarios</uicontrol> to display <xref
            href="scenarios-view.dita#scenarios-view">this view</xref>. Click the <uicontrol><image
              href="../img/NewScenarioDrop.png"/>New Scenario</uicontrol> drop-down menu button and
          select <uicontrol>XProc transformation</uicontrol>.</li>
      </ul></p>
    <p id="p_xzl_cgk_54b">Both methods open the <uicontrol>New Scenario</uicontrol> dialog box.</p>
    <p conkeyref="reusables-transforming-documents/name-storage-options"
      product="author developer editor" id="p_yzl_cgk_54b"/>
    <p product="authorEclipse developerEclipse editorEclipse" id="p_zzl_cgk_54b">The upper part of the dialog box allows
      you to specify the <uicontrol>Name</uicontrol> of the transformation scenario.</p>
    <p id="p_a1m_cgk_54b">The lower part of the dialog box contains several tabs that allow you to configure the
      options that control the transformation.</p>
  </body>
